{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Animation editor"], "type": "title", "extent": [0, 21], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [77, 533], "text": ["The animation editor lets you view and edit animated parameters and how\nHoudini fills in the transitions between keyframes. You can use the\n", {"text": ["graph editor"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/changraph", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "changraph"}, "  view (shows changes in parameter values over time as a graph), the ", {"text": ["parameter table"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/chantable", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "chantable"}, "  view (shows parameter values at\neach keyframe in a table), or the ", {"text": ["dopesheet"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/dopesheet", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "dopesheet"}, "  view to edit animation. To switch between these views, use the pop-up menu at the top left of the pane."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [533, 571], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/images/ui/channel_graph.png", "scheme": "Image", "type": "link", "value": "/images/ui/channel_graph.png"}]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [582, 937], "text": ["You can click ", {"keys": ["RMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " on a channel group in the animation editor and choose ", {"text": ["Motion Effects"], "type": "ui"}, " > ", {"text": ["Create Clip"], "type": "ui"}, " to create a single ", {"text": ["Channel CHOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/chop/channel", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/chop/channel"}, ", moving all the channels in that group to it. Alternatively, if you have multiple channels in the channel list on the playbar, you can also do the same by right-clicking on the playbar."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [937, 1088], "text": ["To create channel groups for a particular node, you can click ", {"keys": ["RMB"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " on the node in the Network View and choose ", {"text": ["Create Nested Channel Groups"], "type": "ui"}, ". "]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [1088, 1307], "text": ["The animation editor can have a sub-pane containing a  ", {"text": ["channel list"], "fullpath": "/ref/panes/chanlist", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "chanlist"}, " . If you already have a channel list pane open, drag the divider divider left to hide the animation editor\u2019s channel list sub-pane."]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Tips"], "extent": [571, 582], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1376, 1418], "text": ["Switches the pane to graph view."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [1347, 1376], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/panes/CHANNELS/view_graph", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "CHANNELS/view_graph"}]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1446, 1488], "text": ["Switches the pane to table view."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [1418, 1446], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/panes/CHANNELS/view_table", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "CHANNELS/view_table"}]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1520, 1575], "text": ["Switches the pane to dopesheet view."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [1488, 1520], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/panes/CHANNELS/view_dopesheet", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "CHANNELS/view_dopesheet"}]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1599, 1727], "text": ["Lets you choose whether you want to view all channels on one graph, or each channel separately on an individual graph."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [1575, 1599], "text": ["Channel drop-down menu"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1749, 1918], "text": ["This menu is enabled when you choose ", {"text": ["Graph Per Channel"], "type": "ui"}, " in the channel drop down menu. It allows you to choose how many graphs you wish to view in the pane."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [1727, 1749], "text": ["Graph drop-down menu"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1937, 2051], "text": ["Homes all channels by panning and zooming the graph to show all keys in the current graph or all graphs."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [1918, 1937], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/panes/IMAGE/home", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "IMAGE/home"}]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2075, 2148], "text": ["Pans and zooms the graph to keep all horizontal values visible."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [2051, 2075], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/panes/BUTTONS/adapt_h", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "BUTTONS/adapt_h"}]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2172, 2243], "text": ["Pans and zooms the graph to keep all vertical values visible."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [2148, 2172], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/panes/BUTTONS/adapt_v", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "BUTTONS/adapt_v"}]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2266, 2326], "text": ["Displays the start and end frames of the sequence."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [2243, 2266], "text": ["Start Frame/End Frame"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2356, 2397], "text": ["Jumps to the previous keyframe."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [2326, 2356], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/panes/PLAYBAR/keyframe_prev", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "PLAYBAR/keyframe_prev"}]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2427, 2464], "text": ["Jumps to the next keyframe."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [2397, 2427], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/panes/PLAYBAR/keyframe_next", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "PLAYBAR/keyframe_next"}]}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2485, 2521], "text": ["Launches the help browser."]}], "indent": 0, "type": "dt", "extent": [2464, 2485], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/ref/panes/BUTTONS/help", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "BUTTONS/help"}]}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Common toolbar controls"], "extent": [1307, 1347], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": "toolbar"}, {"body": [{"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [2544, 2889], "text": ["All of the channels in Houdini are default bezier. The buttons on the function toolbar do not change the type of curve. For example, in earlier versions clicking the line button would set the mathematical equation for the channel to become linear. Now when you click the line button the curve will remain bezier and the handles will line up. "]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [2895, 3004], "text": ["You can still change the type of curve by selecting a different one from ", {"text": ["Function"], "type": "ui"}, " pop-up menu. "]}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "note", "extent": [2889, 2895]}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "note_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Function toolbar"], "extent": [2521, 2544], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [3042, 3304], "text": ["The timeline slider below the graph controls the range of frames\ndisplayed in the graph. Drag the left edge to change the first frame\nshown in the graph. Drag the right edge to change the last frame\nshown. Drag the middle to move the range along the timeline."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [3304, 3405], "text": ["You can also type exact start and end frame numbers in the text\nboxes on either side of the slider."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [3405, 3462], "text": ["For more information see ", {"text": ["playbar"], "fullpath": "/anim/playbar", "scheme": null, "type": "link", "value": "/anim/playbar"}, " help."]}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Frame range slider"], "extent": [3004, 3042], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": "framerange"}], "type": "root", "attrs": {"subtopics_title": "Views", "helpid": "h.pane.channeleditor"}, "title": ["Animation editor"]}